              <h3 id="class-classname">class-[classname]</h3><p>Adds a class (whatever value is in place of <code>[classname]</code>) on the element when the value evaluates to true and removes that class if the value evaluates to false.</p>
<pre><code class="language-html">&lt;li rv-class-completed=&quot;todo.done&quot;&gt;{ todo.name }&lt;/li&gt;
</code></pre>

            </section>
            <section class="my-5">
              <h3 id="add-class">add-class</h3><p>Adds the value of the attribute to the class. Instead of <code>class-[classname]</code> the classname is setted by the attribute value and not by the star value.</p>
<pre><code class="language-html">&lt;ul&gt;
  &lt;li rv-each-todo=&quot;todos&quot;&gt;
    &lt;div rv-add-class=&quot;todo.state&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
</code></pre>

            </section>
