              <h3 id="assign">assign</h3><p>Assign a value in your model. The value you want to assign must be an object and will be concatenate with your model. You can also pass a JSON string.</p>
<pre><code class="language-html">&lt;div rv-assign='{&quot;newValue&quot;: &quot;hello&quot;, &quot;anotherNewValue&quot;: &quot;world&quot;}'&gt;{newValue} {anotherNewValue}!&lt;/div&gt;
</code></pre>

